Package com.i2group.apollo.model.builders.propertyvalue.typed

Contains builders for creating property values of specific types to be used as item data in i2 Analyze.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryDocumentPropertyValueBuilder
    An IBuilder for creating SimplePropertyValues that actually contain DocumentPropertyValues.
    DatePropertyValueBuilder
    An IBuilder for creating SimplePropertyValues that contain values of type LogicalType.DATE.
    DateTimePropertyValueBuilder
    An IBuilder for creating CompoundPropertyValues that contain values of type LogicalType.DATE_AND_TIME.
    GeospatialPropertyValueBuilder
    An IBuilder for creating ComplexPropertyValues that contain values of type LogicalType.GEOSPATIAL.
    TimePropertyValueBuilder
    An IBuilder for creating SimplePropertyValues that contain values of type LogicalType.TIME.
